      "body" : "Question here, what do you mean when you say Spring supports JSR? Doesn&#39;t the container support JSR independent of Spring, and a requirement for the container to be J2EE compliant? Do you mean that it wraps the functionality? If Spring didn&#39;t &quot;support&quot; it, wouldn&#39;t the annotation from javax still work by default?"
