    "answer_id" : 33753519,
    "question_id" : 7142622,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>The key difference(noticed when reading the <a href=\"http://docs.spring.io/spring/docs/3.2.x/spring-framework-reference/html/beans.html#beans-standard-annotations-limitations\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Spring Docs</a>) between <code>@Autowired</code> and <code>@Inject</code> is that, <code>@Autowired</code> has the 'required' attribute while the @Inject has no 'required' attribute.</p>\n"
